{"tid":231253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中學係紅十字會YU既入一入黎","createTime":"2017-05-06T01:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T11:10:29.000Z","uid":24721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53e247aba2ca1771b500b6c1d980928c4a8352be","tid":231253,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:46:34.000Z","msg":"假設你要勸人捐血<br />\n你會點講？<br />\n真係用人道精神同捐血救人就得？<br />\n生命係平等人命關天唔應該分D血比咩人？<br />\n<br />\n我本身都係用呢幾句黎說服自己講個D所謂反捐血運動好不仁不義<br />\n<br />\n但巴打一句捐錢都可以救人(標靶藥事件)同睇下香港既醫療同出入境管制我就真係駁唔到<br />\n當個政府同大陸社會都唔當香港人命係關天，唔將唔同既人生命視作平等，我又何苦係唔平衡既社會上為人捐獻？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係勸人唔好捐<br />\n我始終覺得捐血係應該做，係救人一命<br />\n我亦鼓勵人去捐<br />\n但如果人地咁問起我，我真係答唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都想做好人"},{"pid":"3f488c72de5ab447172ad3d2dd84bf0739589564","tid":231253,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:50:04.000Z","msg":"我想駁連登仔<br />\n但除左用:&quot;萬一有事既係你自己或者你屋企人&quot; 呢句恐嚇之外，根本入唔到"},{"pid":"0b514efc59e6e3205f0f709b15fd296f5090fc6c","tid":231253,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a2cb2e2dc2d19d632e3e99f8738a9bec4ad29b","tid":231253,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925b5de6af65bf275921d7b8fb7ef735a36a7e2f","tid":231253,"uid":17319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"唔洗駁<br />\n退會保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0bf779a93206fdf8765af5b5eeacb794715add","tid":231253,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗駁<br />\n退會保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捐血根本唔關YU事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af757e61d04dd22d39bd4e24d4e371f67787308","tid":231253,"uid":17319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔洗駁<br />\n退會保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捐血根本唔關YU事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不了 童軍 女童 紅十都係紅底<br />\n成日幫手去政府大型活動撐場 俾人強姦"},{"pid":"0b8ad973810a375bf847e7399cba2779e778795d","tid":231253,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09f16615496fca504e86a0795eb345e1f3678b57","tid":231253,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"浪子回頭金不換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}